Distribution map of 
<taxonomicName authority="Reitter, 1913" authorityName="Reitter" authorityYear="1913" class="Insecta" family="Chrysomelidae" genus="Belarima" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Belarima violacea" order="Coleoptera" pageId="0" pageNumber="125" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="violacea">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="125">Belarima violacea</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(Lucas). Red line: Algerian current (see text).
</paragraph>
